Package: cnum
Type: Package
Title: Chinese Numerals in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Elgar Teo
Maintainer: Elgar Teo <elgarteo@connect.hku.hk>
URL: https://github.com/elgarteo/cnum/
BugReports: https://github.com/elgarteo/cnum/issues
Description: This R package provides useful functions to work with Chinese numerals in R,
    such as conversion between Chinese numerals and Arabic numerals as well as detection and
    extraction of Chinese numerals in character objects and string.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R(>= 2.10)
Imports:
    stringr
Suggests:
    magrittr
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
